'''''The Lord of the Rings: Middle-Earth Defense''''' is a tower-defence game for the iPhone and iPod Touch, created by [[Glu Games]]. It offers 18 stages, stretched across seven memorable locations from the books and film trilogy, such as the Tower of [[Orthanc]] and [[Minas Tirith]].

